  </div>
  <div class="faq-list">
    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What is an Applicant Tracking System? <span class="arrow">▼</span></button>
      <div class="faq-a">An ATS is software that automates and manages the recruitment process — from job posting and application collection to candidate tracking, interview scheduling, and hiring decisions. HireTrack makes all of this intuitive and visual.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Do candidates need to create an account? <span class="arrow">▼</span></button>
      <div class="faq-a">Yes. Candidates register for a free account to browse open positions, submit applications, upload their resume, and track their application status in real time.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Can I use HireTrack for free? <span class="arrow">▼</span></button>
      <div class="faq-a">Absolutely. Our Starter plan is completely free with up to 5 active jobs and 50 candidates per month. No credit card required to start.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How does the Kanban pipeline work? <span class="arrow">▼</span></button>
      <div class="faq-a">Candidates are organized into 7 stages: Applied → Screening → Technical Interview → HR Interview → Offer → Hired → Rejected. Recruiters can move candidates between stages with a dropdown, and all updates are stored instantly in the database.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Is my data secure? <span class="arrow">▼</span></button>
      <div class="faq-a">Yes. HireTrack uses JWT authentication, bcrypt password hashing, role-based access control, and secure HTTP-only cookies. Your data is never shared with third parties.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

